Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把它放滿整個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便籤都放好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是七夕 拿便籤有什麼用啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以掛在許願樹上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:55.74,SPEC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(545,55)\fs15\be2\fad(200,0)}許願樹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:55.74,SPEC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(545,115)\be2\fad(200,0)}將寫上願望的便籤\N掛在這棵樹上\N聖誕老人就會為你\N實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想為那些尋找救贖的人實現一個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為聖誕禮物送給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:00:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.69,0:00:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現聖誕節的願望 也是神明的工作啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:48.11,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}聖誕節當天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:48.22,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 雖然回收了便籤…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中的要少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是免費實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是寫上「想變成美女」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「想變成有錢人」這類的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也無能為力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且名字都沒寫 怎麼幫他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 還以為會人手不足特地多叫人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒學姐 知道委託人的便籤 只有這兩張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:19.10,SPEC3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,85)\fad(200,0)}請救救爸爸的咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:19.10,SPEC3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(540,85)\fad(200,0)}急募女服務生！因為感冒店內人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫助咖啡店和蛋糕店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就它們了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個都幫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這麼多人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就兵分兩路地去實現他們的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這倆店…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是正對著的兩家店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我們是競爭對手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,競爭對手？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一決勝負吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣 我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有人向我們提出比賽我們就不能退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 有獎品的話應該會更有幹勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}（獎品）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了就可以隨便使喚他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…不是來實現願望的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:22.50,SPEC4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(285,175)\fad(0,200)\frz5\fry-20\fs13\be2}愛麗絲咖啡店\N今日4時起包場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 讓這家店熱鬧起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美 美緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 櫻守祭那時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要拯救這家咖啡店的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來實現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張便籤…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但勞煩美緒大人大駕…誠惶誠恐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 真是家寒酸的店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思真是太破舊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才有復興的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能輸給對面的蛋糕店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺挺不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿成這樣要幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵查啊偵查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能暴露身份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們兩個是戀人關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節這樣才正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你臉紅什麼啊豬太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是裝裝樣子罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 客人還不少嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,價格適宜 種類豐富
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表也沒什麼缺點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵是味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 不願意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家店不可小視啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你們是情侶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在舉行情侶限定的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起吃這根巧克力棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在覺得是極限的地方停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據所剩的長度 我們將送上禮品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事誰會做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位是初次約會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話可能有點勉強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說不參加的話就不算情侶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我挑戰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先開始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一個聖誕蛋糕怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:07:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個好像都很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我蛋糕 還有烤豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝 謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到變態能量了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要放棄嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛啊 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂戶同學 美緒學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}嘁 沒想到會暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了 豬太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒學姐老是和太郎在一起 太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對面那家店著實是個強敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我想個好主意 現在馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不講理啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一杯本店推薦的王室奶茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我父親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 真是悠哉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 現在只能實行新菜單作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了都交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒大人親手做的料理？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算現在這家店立馬倒閉也無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏賊墨義麵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奶油蛋黃義麵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧豬太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張嘴 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火山爆發！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在口中擴散開來的甘醇苦味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直刺舌頭的香辛料的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是義麵界的黑船開國啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒大人的…特製奶油蛋黃義麵…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能把人感動到這份上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 這可是美緒大人親手做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 爸爸也一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃得都暈過去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一個本店推薦的蛋糕怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 從現在開始咖啡半價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕讚限時優惠中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限時優惠 還真想得出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要超過他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些東西菜單裡有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠這些就能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的東西全都2元出售
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限時優惠大搶購哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2元也太低了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店裡的東西就是客人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大賣一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2元也太犯規了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位注意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在買附贈美少女的魔法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 大家都在等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變好吃 變好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你也跟著做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…變 變好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lovelove
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,spice！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我們也祭出王牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華麗地光臨又小又髒的庶民小店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連我也要…穿成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個 就這樣給我去拉男人去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪倒在我的魅力之下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 馬上會被人家發現我是男生的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像還不太清楚自己的女裝素質啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有男人會看穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一看啊看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多可愛的女生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚民們 盡情地崇拜我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點給我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是太丟人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去就要輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼只有這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成熟的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成熟的 魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別限時優惠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成熟的諾亞也掀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此刺激強烈的風景…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:12:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒叫你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們也來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這實在是太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無權拒絕！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成熟的美腿讓人忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘿莉的腿也不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 這個女生更…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生好可怕好可怕好可怕好可怕 好可怕啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 終於結束了 結果到底是哪邊贏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 就不要提這個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾亞和大家在一起很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來辰吉人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已經關門了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 有預約過4點開始的包場的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 包場？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是生日派對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是聖誕派對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的一個女生的生日和聖誕是同一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要作為生日來好好慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算現在開始做也趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 只能先道歉再拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日派對照常進行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進行 絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 來做吧 派對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 庶民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辰…美小姐 料理拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店裡的準備就由我和結野來做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間宮同學和柊學姐去買蛋糕來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday dear ——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——mio
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(341,328)}美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 能讓他們高興真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子看起來非常開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神的字典裡沒有不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday dear mio
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小滿老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 一臉複雜的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天難道說 是石動學姐的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是美緒並不喜歡自己的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小時候開始就一個人過生日的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今年不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心願嗎 說不定其實就只是想和大家在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MM小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別給我忘了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點就在社團教室沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 之後就是如何不讓學姐發現來準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石動學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 葉山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎他啊 說「今天因為那個貧乳累死了 真不爽」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭取時間 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛 剛才的是事實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 你這洗衣板少女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你沒事亂來我已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 是什麼啊 那個胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 呀 沒胸部的小美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅殺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點也沒有生氣 所以站住 你這大變態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}絕對是騙人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:26.59,SPEC5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(356,109,345,83)\frz25}加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:26.59,SPEC5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(455,245,444,219)\frz25}還差一點了\N祝你好運！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你逃到哪裡 都要把你抹殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}辰吉 快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經逃不掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認命吧 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老實實說出來不就好了 「是我生日」這幾個字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很簡單的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己的願望都不能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又為什麼要去實現別人的願望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次每次 都是只關心別人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又不說關鍵的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在同在一個社團的份上 就聽聽你的遺言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 學姐你覺得我怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話一直沒有對學姐說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷 冷不防的說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個時候 說這種事 有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是 沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你 你 你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能抓到我的話就來抓抓看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是到地獄的盡頭 也不會放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 你這垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這臭豬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我費這麼大工夫 你這臭垃圾變態豬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 是學姐的生日對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豬太郎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家就想搞個驚喜派對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你可能不喜歡這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是學姐出生的 特別的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜 美緒姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是 這個該說是不一樣呢 那個… 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:34.40,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:39.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快來一口氣吹滅掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:41.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是主角的工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:49.09,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這之前還有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:56.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滅掉蠟燭的火之前 要先把這東西的生命之火滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.53,0:21:59.61,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話很有趣呢 哈哈 哈哈 哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:01.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我是在開玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:04.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是喜日啊 喜日…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.94,0:22:13.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:17.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:22.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday dear mio
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:27.92,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:37.53,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:39.12,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜的說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.51,0:22:40.97,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜 美緒學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.69,0:22:43.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:03.70,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:11.24,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有東西 想要送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:14.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是 我送給你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:22.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕禮物喲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.05,0:23:28.42,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈 痛並快樂著
